&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;u&gt;Follow-up labs&lt;/u&gt;. Your next set of lab work will be due &lt;strong&gt;6-8 weeks&lt;/strong&gt; after starting your program. This step ensures that your hormones are being optimized and you are feeling your best.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;
